    "field_description": "Customers’ attention spans are dwindling. Traditional media channels are unable to hold their interest any more. So, the key to engaging with our customers was to find out where they were spending their time. We undertook a data-driven approach and studied their content consumption behaviour. The result was emphatic – more Citi customers were on social media than ever before. A 5X jump in video consumption, with 8.5 hours of content consumed every month, led us to adopt a ‘Video First’ approach to reach out to them. Read on to find out how we leveraged it. ",
